=== Noun ===
'''mail''' (''Uncountable'')

# regular [[delivery]] of [[letter]]s and small [[parcel]]s, see also [[post]]
# the [[organisation]] which delivers such (e.g. in Britain the Royal Mail)
# abbreviated from “electronic mail”, a store and forward message service on a [[computer]], often using the Internet
# any of several types of [[armour]]

